{"tid":2013183,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有無人好鐘意食燉冰強?","createTime":"2020-05-12T06:47:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T10:01:55.000Z","uid":23707,"like":120,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"95a8d68316a3312bc7e225b094f8b34338c522bd","tid":2013183,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:47:18.000Z","msg":"冰糖燉強食譜(Google)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-global.cpcdn.com/recipes/b5ee04cf45766874/751x532cq70/%E9%A4%8A%E9%A1%8F%E7%94%9C%E9%BB%9E%E5%86%B0%E8%8A%B1%E7%87%89%E8%9B%8B-%E9%A3%9F%E8%AD%9C%E6%88%90%E5%93%81%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-global.cpcdn.com%2Frecipes%2Fb5ee04cf45766874%2F751x532cq70%2F%25E9%25A4%258A%25E9%25A1%258F%25E7%2594%259C%25E9%25BB%259E%25E5%2586%25B0%25E8%258A%25B1%25E7%2587%2589%25E8%259B%258B-%25E9%25A3%259F%25E8%25AD%259C%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2593%2581%25E7%2585%25A7%25E7%2589%2587.jpg&h=9b9e4aa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一般食材<br />\n雞蛋 3 g<br />\n冰糖 50 克<br />\n清水 230 公升<br />\n<br />\n步驟<br />\n1.將水和冰糖放入小鍋內，用中火煮至糖溶化，待涼備用<br />\n2.將雞蛋打發，加入牛奶、糖水，拌勻<br />\n3.用篩過濾，倒入容器內，<br />\n4.用保鮮膜包好，用中火蒸8分鐘，然後離火，一直蓋著蓋悶15分鐘即成！"},{"pid":"5c38af3a1921e93472fe7992778983ed26739a4c","tid":2013183,"uid":70973,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:49:09.000Z","msg":"個名改得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5661ef332b0b7bdc18f68bd15ab339124ac7afac","tid":2013183,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:49:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4593e21b84fd9415f686d39f38