牛奶、糖水，拌勻<br />\n3.用篩過濾，倒入容器內，<br />\n4.用保鮮膜包好，用中火蒸8分鐘，然後離火，一直蓋著蓋悶15分鐘即成！</blockquote>一茶匙雞蛋同230公升水？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>可能佢想打3隻蛋掛<br />\ni dont care</blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:58:15.000Z","msg":"重點好似唔係幾多隻蛋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T00:13:41.000Z","msg":"多强230公升水咪合理啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17e70912e692cfd304b1a01c641a153d76417aab","tid":2013183,"uid":334025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T01:06:07.000Z","msg":"230公升要幾個浴缸先裝到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af69aba40c3b985a4958653c307ca7813df1574","tid":2013183,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T01:56:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c2eb3acf05de244c44a59ab8eafe976c14bac2","tid":2013183,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T09:06:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73869d25682346d55d2cd2a4ef14b9943d386d2e","tid":2013183,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T09:08:15.000Z","msg":"牛奶 並沒有"},{"pid":"b75d4afb87d62f2464db79dbb4682689443efdc4","tid":2013183,"uid":117225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca029d4a3abac78f7114a78584955ea0f07c16ec","tid":2013183,"uid":156618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0203cbb09bb9fa64a47f6ffd73f33febb4808c6","tid":2013183,"uid":204539,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:52:10.000Z","msg":"雞蛋 3 g<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冰糖 50 克<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n清水 230 公升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkg